import React, { Component } from 'react';
import './App.css';

import {
    Container,
    Icon,
    Link,
    List,
    ListItem,
    Offcanvas,
    OffcanvasContainer,
    Navbar,
    NavbarContainer,
    NavbarSticky,
    Section,
} from 'uikit-react';

class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
        <OffcanvasContainer>
        <Section>
        <NavbarSticky options="animation: uk-animation-slide-top; cls-inactive: uk-navbar-transparent uk-light; top: 556;">
          <NavbarContainer>
          <Navbar>
          <ListItem>
          <Link toggleOptions="target: #menu;" href="#">
          <Icon options="menu" button />
      </Link>
      </ListItem>
      </Navbar>
      </NavbarContainer>
      </NavbarSticky>
      <Offcanvas id="menu" options="overlay: true">
          <List type="divider">
          <ListItem>
          <Link href="/">Home</Link>
          </ListItem>
          </List>
          </Offcanvas>
          </Section>
          </OffcanvasContainer>
    );
  }
}

export default App;
